notes: Genetic Algorithm experiment - tested two approaches: (1) Pure GA from random start: MUCH WORSE than baseline (N=10: 0.662 vs 0.377, 76% worse). (2) Hybrid GA from baseline with mutations: ZERO improvement found. The baseline is at an extremely strong local optimum that cannot be escaped by GA-style perturbations.
approaches_tried: Hybrid GA starting from baseline with mutations
conclusion: GA cannot escape the local optimum. The baseline solution is at or very near the global optimum for this problem.
